      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 68.11 - 老子 68.12</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>是謂用人之力，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thus we say, 'Men's wills he bends, That they with him unite.'</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
