      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 68.13 - 老子 68.14</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>是謂配天古之極。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thus we say, 'Like Heaven's his ends, No sage of old more bright.'</seg>
